<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Zephaniah on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/</link><description>Recent content in Zephaniah on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Zephaniah 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="zephaniah-chapter-1">Zephaniah Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpFirst" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>A Message from the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> to Zephaniah Son of Cushi&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>(&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Son of Gedaliah Son of Amariah&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height: 115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>) Son of Hezekiah &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-bottom:0in; text-align:center'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family: "Times New Roman",serif'>at &lt;b>the Time of Josiah Son of Amon, King of Judah&lt;/b>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="the-coming-judgment-on-judah">The Coming Judgment on Judah&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“I’ll remove everything &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      from the earth,”&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> says,&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Zephaniah 2</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-02/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-02/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="zephaniah-chapter-2">Zephaniah Chapter 2&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="a-call-for-repentance">A Call for Repentance&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122959205">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Get together, &lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      go ahead, assemble, shameless nation,&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>                  2&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>before the decree takes effect—&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            before that day &lt;i>of repentance&lt;/i> passes by like chaff—&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            before the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>’s burning anger comes down on you.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Look to him,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      you humble in the land&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Zephaniah 3</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-03/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cnt-ot/zephaniah/chapter-03/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="zephaniah-chapter-3">Zephaniah Chapter 3&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="the-future-of-jerusalem">The Future of Jerusalem&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;a name="_Hlk122958634">&lt;span class="verse verse-v1" id="v1">&lt;sup class="verse-num">1&lt;/sup> &lt;/a>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Misfortune awaits the rebellious, defiled, tyrannical city, &lt;i>Jerusalem,&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      &lt;/span>&lt;span class="verse verse-v2" id="v2">&lt;sup class="verse-num">2&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>that wouldn’t take advice or accept instruction,&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      that didn’t trust in the L&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:9.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>ORD&lt;/span>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt; line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'> or come near to its God.&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span class="verse verse-v3" id="v3">&lt;sup class="verse-num">3&lt;/sup> &lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Its officials are roaring lions;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>its judges are ravening wolves at dusk&lt;/span>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>